ng, and resurfacing, based on road condition assessments.<\/p>\n<p class=\"lc_para\">\u2022LO5: Operate and maintain road maintenance machinery and equipment safely and in accordance with operational guidelines.<\/p>\n<p class=\"lc_para\">\u2022LO6: Apply excavation safety measures and soil stabilization techniques to prevent trench collapse and ensure ground stability.<\/p>\n\n<\/div><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<table border=\"0\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr class=\"lc_table_header\">\n<th rowspan=\"2\" width=\"25%\">Course<\/th>\n<th colspan=\"3\" width=\"45%\"> Duration (8 hours per day)<\/th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\" width=\"30%\">Course Fees (Exclude GST)<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<tr class=\"lc_table_header2\">\n<td>Practical<\/td>\n<td>Theory<\/td>\n<td>Test<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr class=\"lc_tr\">\n<td style=\"background-color: #a4cef0;\" rowspan=\"4\">Essential Road Maintenance<\/td>\n<td rowspan=\"2\"> 4 Days<\/td>\n<td rowspan=\"3\"> 1 Day<\/td>\n<td>1 Day<\/td>\n<td>$ 2,700<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr class=\"lc_tr\"><\/tr>\n<tr class=\"lc_tr\"><\/tr>\n<tr class=\"lc_tr\"><\/tr>\n<tr class=\"lc_tr_alt\"><\/tr>\n<tr class=\"lc_tr_alt\"><\/tr>\n<tr class=\"lc_tr_alt\"><\/tr>\n<tr class=\"lc_tr_alt\"><\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"lc_table_last_line\" colspan=\"7\">\n<div><\/div><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>*Additional Course Training Requests: $200 (Exclude GST) per day.<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<div>Applicants are required to make payments exclusively to the company's designated bank account and obtain an official receipt.<\/div><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<div>\n<p class=\"bold\">For queries on application, please contact:<\/p>\n<p class=\"bold\">Training Coordinator<\/p>\n<p class=\"lc_para\"><span class=\"bold\">Tel:<\/span> 6705 5290 \/ 9749 7241<\/p>\n<p class=\"lc_para\"><span class=\"bold\">Email:<\/span> <a href=\"mailto:training@leychoon.com\">training@leychoon.com<\/a><\/p>\n\n<\/div><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<